[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "薬は作った、爆弾も作った……\nあとは携帯食料ですね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "みんな、どんなものが食べたいんだろ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "拙者の忍びの携帯食、\n兵糧丸を参考にされてはいかがでござるか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "おお……ただの丸いかたまり。\nこれって美味しいの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "食べてみてもいいですか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "拙者が練ったものでよければ、どうぞお試しあれ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "それじゃあ、お言葉に甘えて……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "……ちょっと味気ないですね。\nまずくはないですけど……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "まあ、兵糧丸は腹持ちと栄養重視で、\n味は二の次でござるからなあ……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "とはいえ、味の改善にも取り組んでいるでござる！\nその試作品が、こちら！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "レイニャ",
		"romanized_name": "Lenja",
		"model_path_hash": "5067796612903841500",
		"text": "わあ……色とりどり、たくさんありますね。\nあの、これ、レイニャも食べていいですか……？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "326916344881311074",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "どうぞどうぞ、遠慮なく！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "レイニャ",
		"romanized_name": "Lenja",
		"model_path_hash": "5067796612903841500",
		"text": "じゃあ、この赤くてかわいいのを、いただきます。\nあむ……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "326916344881311074",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "お目が高い！　それは刺激的な食事をと思い、\n激辛にしたものでござるよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レイニャ",
		"romanized_name": "Lenja",
		"model_path_hash": "5067796612903841500",
		"text": "ひゃああああああ！！！\n痛い！　舌が焼き切れそうです……！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "326916344881311074",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "だ、大丈夫？　ほら、牛乳飲んで……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "リラ",
		"romanized_name": "Lila",
		"model_path_hash": "6420784340983749558",
		"text": "ともかく、腹は膨れるのだろう？\nなら、武道会には十分なんじゃないか",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "658330190563200680",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "同感だ。戦場では味より効能が重要だろう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "ええー？　どうせ食べるなら、\nやっぱり美味しいのがいいよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "アタシも！　\n味が良くないと元気出ないよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん、そうだよね……美味しくて栄養もある\n携帯食料のレシピを考えてみるよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "錬金術士の腕の見せどころだね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "あたしも調合手伝うよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……できた！　「みなぎるマフィン」！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うーん、いい匂い！　見た目もいい感じ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "味見してみようよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "いただきます！　……うん、美味しい！　\nこれならきっと、元気出ること間違いなしです！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "リラ",
		"romanized_name": "Lila",
		"model_path_hash": "6420784340983749558",
		"text": "栄養価も十分。保存性も高い。\n砂漠でも持つだろう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "658330190563200680",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "これで、武道会の準備は整いました。\nあとは本番を待つのみです……！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]